text: Stocksville is an unincorporated community in Buncombe County, North Carolina. Located at the intersection of Old Mars Hill Highway (SR 2207) and Murphy Hill Road (SR 2134), near the I-26/US 19/US 23 interchange (exit 17). North Buncombe High School is located nearby. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Buncombe County, North Carolina Category:Unincorporated communities in North Carolina
